        <marginalia hand="Italian">
            <language ident="LA">
                <position book_orientation="0" place="tail">
                    <marginalia_text>Pauci egregij, ac terribiles viri, ingentis victoria[e] auctores: ut aliàs pla[e]runq[ue]. Vnde tales pauci exquisita observatione intime
                        examinandi. Curiosa suo loco Analysis mirificè conducit, pra[e]sertim politica, et stratagematica.</marginalia_text>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>A few eminent and formidable men created a giant victory, just as frequently at other times. Therefore the few such men should be studied 
                closely with scrupulous attention. A careful analysis, at its right place, is singularly useful, especially a political and tactical one.</translation>
        </marginalia>
        
